Modifying the chords by removing & adding a note

    E ––3–––3––                     E ––3–––3––
    B ––1–––1––                     B ––1–––1––
    G ––0–––2–– <= left middle      G ––0–––0––
    D ––3–––3––                     D ––0–––2–– <= left middle
    A –––––––––                     A ––3–––3––
